Summary: Purplish/Red light hoovering over I17-Thunderbird Ave traveling south
divs: Sighting DetailsSeen a light as I left my hm at 9:55pm Pulsating purplish,red light hoovering over I17-Thunderbird traveling south. No aircraft i know can move up,down sideways zoom here & there. I observed it for 5 min with my sister on the phone. I noticed a helicoper was getting close to it but the object tried moving away from helicopter, the ufo finally started moving south in a swirly motion. I wonder if the traffic accident that happened at I17 & Thunderbird had anything to do with the object. Whats going on? there had to be tons of witnesses. Neat but scary
